Dinner in the factory.

01:18:25.720 --> 01:18:27.720
Yeah.

01:18:27.720 --> 01:18:31.720
So when would that have been, do you think? In the 90s? 80s, 90s?

01:18:31.720 --> 01:18:32.720
80s.

01:18:32.720 --> 01:18:35.720
I'm looking at the hair now, I'm thinking that's 80s hair, isn't it?

01:18:35.720 --> 01:18:39.720
Yes, definitely. I don't know exactly when, but in the 80s.

01:18:39.720 --> 01:18:41.720
She looks as if she's having a good time.

